{"type":null,"faqId":10126,"title":"G6-U00如何启用PIN码锁定屏幕？","answer":"<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>1、<span> </span></span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">设置<span>-</span></span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">&gt;</span><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">安全</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">-&gt;</span><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">屏幕锁定</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">-&gt;<b>PIN</b></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>2、<span> </span></span></span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">在“<b>请输入您的<span>PIN</span>”</b>下面的提示框中输入<span>PIN</span>码后继续。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>3、<span> </span></span></span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">再次输入刚才输入的<span>PIN</span>码，点击<b>确定</b>完成对<span>PIN</span>码的设定。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">当点电源键或开关机时，手机会默认进入<span>PIN</span>码解锁界面，输入设定的<span>PIN</span>码后点击“<b>回车键<span></span></b>”解除<span>PIN</span>码的锁定。<span></span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":1,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"705","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396602209000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":36,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"PIN","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}